    <div id="intro">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="col-lg-10 offset-lg-1">
          <p>
            I am a Ph.D. candidate at the <a rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" href="https://lsa.umich.edu/astro">University of Michigan Department of Astronomy</a>, where I work with Prof. <a rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" href="http://www-personal.umich.edu/~ognedin/">Oleg Gnedin</a>. Before coming to Michigan, I received my B.S. degree at <a rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" href="http://astro.pku.edu.cn/">Peking University School of Physics, Department of Astronomy</a> in July 2017. My current research focuses on the formation and evolution of Milky Way-like galaxies using cosmological simulations. <a rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" href="research.html">Click here</a> to view my research in detail.
          </p>
          <center>
            <a href="#" class="btn btn-outline-light" role="button">Curriculum Vitae</a>
